  <brief_title>Efficacy and Safety of Abelmoschus Manihot for IgA Nephropathy</brief_title>
  <official_title>Efficacy and Safety of Abelmoschus Manihot for IgA Nephropathy: a Multicentre, Double-blind, Double-dummy, Randomized Controlled Trial</official_title>
