  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      -IgA nephropathy is the most common primary glomerular disease in China, Huangkui Capsule is
      a single medicament of traditional Chinese medicine consists of Abelmoschus manihot and has
      been widely used to treat kidney disease. The purpose of this study is to evaluate the safety
      and efficacy of Abelmoschus manihot for treating IgA nephropathy in large scale samples with
      long time take.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
